{{> header title=title subtitle="Don't forget to complete your interview" gradient=gradient company_icon_url=company_icon_url}}

<div class="content">
  <p>Hello{{#if interviewee_name}} {{interviewee_name}}{{/if}},</p>

  <p>This is a friendly reminder that you have an outstanding interview{{#if company_name}} with <strong>{{company_name}}</strong>{{/if}} waiting to be completed{{#if due_date}} by <strong>{{due_date}}</strong>{{/if}}. The interview is <strong>{{interview_name}}</strong> for the <strong>{{assessment_name}}</strong> assessment.</p>

  <p>To complete your interview, click the button below:</p>

  {{> button text="Complete Interview" url=interview_url color=button_color}}

  <p style="margin-top: 20px; color: #6c757d; font-size: 13px;"><strong>Alternative access:</strong> If the button doesn't work, copy and paste this link into your browser: {{interview_url}}</p>

  <p style="margin-top: 20px; color: #6c757d; font-size: 13px;"><strong>Need your access code?</strong> If you navigate to the site directly: <span style="font-family: monospace; background: #f8f9fa; padding: 4px 8px; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: 600;">{{access_code}}</span></p>

  <p>Thank you for your time,{{#if sender_name}}<br><strong>{{sender_name}}</strong>{{/if}}{{#if company_name}}<br>{{company_name}}{{/if}}</p>

  <p style="margin-top: 10px; padding-top: 10px; color: #6c757d; font-size: 12px;">If you have any questions or need assistance, please contact{{#if sender_name}} <strong>{{sender_name}}</strong>{{/if}}{{#if sender_email}} at <a href="mailto:{{sender_email}}">{{sender_email}}</a>{{/if}}.</p>
</div>

{{> footer}}
